android {
          compileSdkVersion 22
           buildToolsVersion ""23.0.0""
            defaultConfig {
             minSdkVersion 14 //lower than 14 doesn't support multidex
             targetSdkVersion 22
             // Enabling multidex support.
             multiDexEnabled true
         }
     }
     dependencies {
     compile 'com.android.support:multidex:1.0.1'
     }
